        Inclusion Criteria:

        1.18≤age≤75; 2.Being scheduled to undergo colorectal cancer surgery; 3.Being able to
        complete all the assessment.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Having a history of tumor, mental disorders(including dementia), brain trauma or other
             cerebral diseases;

          2. Having severe depression and anxiety currently;

          3. Having alcohol dependence or other substance dependence;

          4. Having serious physical illness;

          5. Participating in other clinical studies.
